XDrift                  XDrift: Spray-drift Modeling Tools for
                        Landscape-Scale Ecotoxicological Risk
                        Assessment
bands                   Dividing a plane into bands
mindwdist               Calculate the minimum downwind distance between
                        sources and sinks
rautmann90              Calculating spray-drift exposure according to
                        Rautmann (90th percentile)
xspraydrift             Calculating spray-drift exposure with the
                        XSprayDrift model
xspraydriftparameters   XSprayDrift distribution parameters
